For many longtime cable heads, last week=E2=80=99s news of Warner Bros. Dis=
covery=E2=80=99s distribution deal with Charter was unequivocally the talk =
of the town. The Journal, after all, reported ( https://www.wsj.com/busines=
s/media/warner-bros-discovery-signs-new-distribution-deal-with-charter-eba4=
